---
title: 批次處理 vs 串流處理 (Batch vs Stream Processing)
---
flowchart LR
    subgraph BATCH["🗂️ 批次處理 (Batch Processing)"]
        direction TB
        B1["📦 累積資料\n(小時/天)"] --> B2["⚙️ Hadoop MapReduce\n或 Spark batch"]
        B2 --> B3["📊 輸出結果\n(高延遲，高吞吐)"]
    end

    subgraph STREAM["⚡ 串流處理 (Stream Processing)"]
        direction TB
        S1["📡 即時事件流\n(毫秒~秒)"] --> S2["🔄 Spark Structured\nStreaming (micro-batch)"]
        S2 --> S3["📊 即時輸出\n(低延遲，持續更新)"]
    end

    subgraph COMPARE["📋 核心差異"]
        direction TB
        C1["批次：高延遲 / 高吞吐\n✅ 適合：報表、ETL管線"]
        C2["串流：低延遲 / 即時\n✅ 適合：詐欺偵測、即時儀表板"]
    end

    BATCH --> COMPARE
    STREAM --> COMPARE
